.TH MPIX_GPU_query_support 3 "11/8/2022" " " "MPI"
.SH NAME
MPIX_GPU_query_support \-  Returns whether the specific type of GPU is supported 
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
int MPIX_GPU_query_support(int gpu_type, int *is_supported)
.fi
.SH INPUT PARAMETERS
.PD 0
.TP
.B gpu_type 
- MPIX_GPU_SUPPORT_CUDA or MPIX_GPU_SUPPORT_ZE (integer)
.PD 1

.SH OUTPUT PARAMETERS
.PD 0
.TP
.B is_supported 
- true if gpu of given type is supported, false otherwise. (logical)
.PD 1

